I sincerely request the Coke Studios Management to look into setting up a healthy, creative and extremely entertaining festival to bring the world together by Coke Studios from so many countries of the world with extremely entertaining creations attracting people of the world regardless of their mother tongue. Pakistan Coke Studio may be the best of them. I was in
Canada in 1969 when Woodstock Music Festival was held in the US. It was a unique and most famous festival of the creative artists. I think it is about time to have a similar and even better and greater COKE STUDIOS MUSIC FESTIVAL.
